                  Logistics and Supply Chain Benchmarking
               </h4>
               <p>With its archipelagic geography, logistics efficiency is a defining factor of Indonesia’s competitiveness. We benchmark port performance, transport costs, customs clearance times, and logistics infrastructure development.</p>
               <p>Our benchmarking highlights the impact of initiatives under the National Logistics Ecosystem (NLE) and assesses Indonesia’s connectivity improvements against regional peers. The findings support logistics operators and investors in optimizing transport networks and strengthening Indonesia’s role as a regional logistics gateway.</p>
