               <p>By comparing Indonesia’s progress in solar, geothermal, and bioenergy against ASEAN countries, we provide insights that support corporate sustainability and national decarbonization goals. Our benchmarking aligns with Kementerian ESDM (Ministry of Energy and Mineral Resources) to ensure compliance and strategy alignment with Indonesia’s Net Zero 2060 target.</p>
               <h4 class="text-lg lg:text-xl heading-4">
                  Digital and Innovation Benchmarking
               </h4>
               <p>Indonesia’s digital economy is one of the largest and fastest-growing in Southeast Asia. We benchmark digital infrastructure, e-commerce penetration, and technology adoption across key industries such as fintech, logistics, and retail.</p>
               <p>Our analysis covers parameters like cloud usage, data management, and AI readiness, comparing Indonesia’s digital maturity against ASEAN peers. The benchmarking supports organizations in aligning with national initiatives under Making Indonesia 4.0 and Digital Indonesia Framework, driving competitiveness in the fourth industrial revolution.</p>

