                  Healthcare and Consumer Market Benchmarking
               </h4>
               <p>Indonesia’s healthcare and consumer markets are expanding due to demographic growth and urbanization. We benchmark hospital capacity, pharmaceutical production, and healthcare access relative to ASEAN standards.</p>
               <p>In consumer markets, we assess spending patterns, brand competitiveness, and digital retail penetration. These insights help multinational and domestic companies refine strategies for market entry, product localization, and customer engagement within Indonesia’s dynamic consumer landscape.</p>

