                  Construction and Infrastructure Benchmarking
               </h4>
               <p>As infrastructure development remains a cornerstone of Indonesia’s growth strategy, we benchmark project cost, delivery timelines, and productivity across major public and private projects.</p>
               <p>The assessment includes transport infrastructure, energy facilities, and industrial zone developments. By aligning with Public-Private Partnership (PPP) frameworks and national priorities under Bappenas, our benchmarking enables construction companies and investors to enhance delivery performance and regulatory compliance.</p>

